txt.en: Valdi can be found in Amdân.\n\nYou should talk to Valdi.
DNT - 'You have defeated the Wargs and their sires? Well done, friend. We have dealt a solid blow to the enemy this day.'
'You have defeated the Wargs and their sires? Well done, friend. We have dealt a solid blow to the enemy this day.'

'We shall now strike the source! The fiercest and most deadly of the Warg champions are all kin, results of numerous litters produced by two past champions, Naurnash and Khakrank. Defeating the sires and thinning the pack will go a long way to removing their evil from Azanulbizar.'
The Wargs of Azanulbizar must have their ranks thinned before the major battle takes place.
Wargs can be found at Gadh Ujáf and Zagâf Muzug.\n\nValdi has asked you to defeat Wargs and their sires.
